OL,3,C'There's certain places I won't go':
OL,4,CSpiking victim tells of lasting impact
OL,6,FA victim of drink spiking in Jersey
OL,7,Fwants to help raise awareness of the
OL,8,Fdangers, but also what to do if you
OL,9,Ffear you have been spiked.
OL,11,FKim Campbell found when she got home
OL,12,Ffrom having dinner and drinks with a
OL,13,Ffriend, she had lost all feeling in
OL,14,Fher body from the neck down.
OL,16,FShe found she was unable to move and
OL,17,Fher friend had to call the fire
OL,18,Fbrigade to break into her house so the
OL,19,Fambulance service could take her
OL,20,Fstraight to the hospital.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
