OL,3,C'There's certain places I won't go':
OL,4,CSpiking victim tells of lasting impact
OL,6,FKim said: "People feel embarrassed,
OL,7,Fyou blame yourself and for me, I was
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital and assumed that
OL,9,Fthey'd taken blood tests.
OL,11,F"At the time the Doctor who saw me
OL,12,Fsaid I was the fourth that evening,
OL,13,Fthat night, who had been brought in -
OL,14,Fnot from the same place, but from the
OL,15,Fisland."
OL,17,FShe added, the thought of what could
OL,18,Fhave happened has had a huge impact on
OL,19,Fher life.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
