OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778544176
OL,3,C'There's certain places I won't go':
OL,4,CSpiking victim tells of lasting impact
OL,6,F"There's certain places I won't go,
OL,7,Fthat I should be able to. (It's
OL,8,Faffected) my children, because I've
OL,9,Fput that fear, in a way onto my
OL,10,Fchildren. That you have to be so
OL,11,Fcareful when you're out, and that the
OL,12,Fonus is on us and you can't just be
OL,13,Fout having fun."
OL,15,F"I almost became a prisoner in my own
OL,16,Fhome. I hadn't realised at the time,
OL,17,Fbut it was months and months before I
OL,18,Fthought, yes I can actually go out, I
OL,19,Fcan trust.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
