OL,3,C'There's certain places I won't go':
OL,4,CSpiking victim tells of lasting impact
OL,6,F"So I just feel we have to stop this.
OL,7,FWe have to get people reporting and
OL,8,Frealising the seriousness of this. "
OL,10,FLatest statistics from Jersey show
OL,11,Fsince 2015:
OL,13,FJersey's Home Affairs Minister, Deputy
OL,14,FMary le Hegerat said: "The difficulty
OL,15,Fthat we have is actually proving the
OL,16,Foffence.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
