OL,3,C'There's certain places I won't go':
OL,4,CSpiking victim tells of lasting impact
OL,6,F"It's imperative that the person seeks
OL,7,Fmedical help, so in an ideal world
OL,8,Fthat's going to the hospital because
OL,9,Fwe need people to get a blood test in
OL,10,Forder to prove they have something in
OL,11,Ftheir body that shouldn't be there."
OL,13,FShe added: "So I think the thing is
OL,14,Ffor me there's a lot of statistics and
OL,15,Fthey're high, but I want to resolve
OL,16,Fthe issue of us not being able to move
OL,17,Fthese forward "
