OL,3,C'There's certain places I won't go':
OL,4,CSpiking victim tells of lasting impact
OL,6,FKim did not realise she needed to
OL,7,Fcontact the police to get tested and
OL,8,Fassumed it had been done at the
OL,9,Fhospital, and by the time she did, it
OL,10,Fwas too late and any substance would
OL,11,Fhave left her system.
OL,13,FJersey and Guernsey police have
OL,14,Fconfirmed that potential spiking
OL,15,Fvictims need to report the alleged
OL,16,Fcrime to them as soon as possible, to
OL,17,Fget the necessary tests.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
