OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778544176
OL,3,C'There's certain places I won't go':
OL,4,CSpiking victim tells of lasting impact
OL,6,FThese include blood tests within 3
OL,7,Fdays, urine tests within 5 days and
OL,8,Fthey can consider a hair sample which
OL,9,Fcan be taken 4-6 weeks after the
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,FThe police in both jurisdictions have
OL,13,Fconfirmed that the hospital will not
OL,14,Fautomatically do a blood test if the
OL,15,Fvictim is in hospital, and instead the
OL,16,Fpolice need to be contacted.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
